item.title: ABOUT
item.content:encoded:
Steven U. | New York | Photographer | Traveler

Hello,

My name is Steven U. I am a photographer based in Manhattan, New York.

I love to travel and take pictures of anything that seems interesting.

Some of my favorite countries that I’ve traveled to were Thailand, Colombia, and Dubai.

If you like anime and traveling, we’ll be best friends.
